scenes.description: Amelia Watson investigates Ninomae Ina'nis, testing her halo's physics with a 'scientific dunk' before the other members intervene.
The Hololive Myth members gather to 'investigate' Amelia, examining her outfit and gear, then transition to preparing for their first 3D game.
Takanashi Kiara introduces and explains the rules of 'Telephone Charades', and the group begins the first round with the keyword 'Octopus'.
